Class FullCacheImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • biz.gabrys.lesscss.extended.compiler.cache.FullCacheImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompilationDateCache, CompiledCodeCache, DeletableCache, FullCache, SourceCodeCache, SourceImportsCache, SourceModificationDateCache

    public class FullCacheImpl
extends Object
implements FullCache, DeletableCache
    Full cache implementation based on the DataStorage. It stores files in the flat structure.
